=== Assessment Schedule

    - *Baseline*: Full clinical assessment, baseline functional status (Bell scale, SF-36, DSQ-PEM)
    - *Quarterly (every 3 months)*: Functional reassessment, infection history review
    - *Continuous*: Infection documentation by patient (illness diary or symptom tracker app)
Duration: 3 years per participant.


